.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, western, scientific
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, rock-climbing
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, journalist
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the architect is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person watching scientific movies##2
5. the person watching western movies is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Movie-Genre      | comedy       | western      | scientific      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | rock-climbing | chess      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | rock          | folk       |

