3. the person eating avocado is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person eating banana is the social-worker##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | drawing       | traveling       | chess    |
