.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-15::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, cherry, potato
City: marseilles, hannover, miami
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, spanish
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, subway, train
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person traveling to miami and the spanish##2
3. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the person traveling to miami and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the person traveling to hannover is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
| City   | miami  | hannover     | marseilles |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | spanish   |
| Transport     | train   | subway   | bike      |

