3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, rat
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bluemaster, old-henry
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, tram
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the horse##2
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is the person driving the boat##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby       | singing | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Pet         | horse   | rat       | mouse        |
| Cigar       | old-henry | blend   | bluemaster         |
| Transport   | tram    | train     | boat         |

